.36 万亿元，同比少增 5418 亿元。分部门看，住户贷款增加 3672 亿元，其中，短期贷款增加 1988 亿元，中长期贷款增加 1684 亿元；企（事）业单位贷款增加 8558 亿元，其中，短期贷款增加 350 亿元，中长期贷款增加 7698 亿元，票据融资增加 420 亿元；非银行业金融机构贷款增加 604 亿元。5 月末，外币贷款余额 7215 亿美元，同比下降 20.7%。5 月份外币贷款减少 160 亿美元，同比多减 44 亿美元。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-1e8f8c508dd9978100f806f6e00e7dae_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "56 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/606375117"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4IoO6fjuHeuptXEAMaCDk3MDMwMjcyIL/GoKQGMAA4ogNAGnIIOTcwMzAyNzJ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "27_1686683176.584484", "card_id": "Q_603686622", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 32}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "对于装修人群来说，有哪些家电适合趁着 618 购入？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-9ec3677621d05051be7e6ed6a7a9b6ae_1440w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "56 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/603686622"}}, "attached_info": "Cj0IoO6fjuHeuptXEAMaCDk2NDMzMDE1IKSW0qMGMAA4PkAbcgg5NjQzMzAxNXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "28_1686683176.584715", "card_id": "Q_605319629", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 42}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "你身边获得美国 10 年旅游签的朋友，有哪些共同点？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-fcbf4cc786a514908ea1f29925b4161a_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "55 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/605319629"}}, "attached_info": "Cj0IoO6fjuHeuptXEAMaCD